ZM_JUNGLE_RGE
 This map was released 3 months ago,it was uploaded here on FPSB,but then it was deleted next week because of the screenshots.Now i upload this map the right way so you can enjoy it
 This map is based on tactical teamplay with good teamspirit To survive on this map you should play with somebody,playing on your own on this map doesn't make sense Thechnical: -The map got 64 spawns -The map got HDR -The map got Cubemaps -The map got a custom skybox by HAZEL -The map got custom jungle models by SHIROKO -The map got custom models by me like the bridge or the stone heads -The map got custom nav file -The map got custom scripted sounds and grass For more screenshots visit RussianGermanEnglish's homepage you are allowed to use my content but don't forget to give me credits
